The paper proposes a data structure for storing labeled attributed graphs, which is relevant to database systems (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses operations and queries on the graph data, which relates to information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper proposes a dynamic version of the storage representation, which is relevant to software engineering (cs.SE).
